{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0226eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0226ENG","gazette":"Department of Commerce","title":"Regarding the implementation of the Decision imposing additional duty on steel imports into the United States","date":"18 Mart 2025","bodyHtml":"<p>In accordance with the US Presidential Decree No. 10896, an additional tax of 25% was imposed on steel imports into the U.S regardless of country.</p><p>(including countries with which the USA has an FTA).</p><p>The notification regarding the implementation of this Decision was also published.</p><p>As of March 12, 2025, an additional 25% duty was applied to all&nbsp; steel product groups.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/FR-2025-03-05/pdf/2025-03598.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Click here for the pdf version of the notification.</font></a></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/FR-2025-03-05/html/2025-03598.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Click here for the text version of the notification.</font></a></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">According to the notification, the product groups subject to 25% additional duty are determined as follows.</font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><b style=\"text-de